1255
01:37:06,570 --> 01:37:07,980
也寻找过你
I have chased you.

1256
01:37:11,190 --> 01:37:13,090
我曾试着控制你
I have tried to contain you.

1257
01:37:16,280 --> 01:37:18,210
也试着原谅你
I have tried to forgive you.

1258
01:37:22,650 --> 01:37:27,010
我本以为你是恶魔人
I thought maybe you were the Boogeyman.

1259
01:37:27,580 --> 01:37:28,690
但
No.

1260
01:37:29,490 --> 01:37:34,220
你只是一个将死之人罢了
You're just a man who's about to stop breathing.

1261
01:37:57,590 --> 01:37:58,760
来吧
Do it.

1262
01:38:00,150 --> 01:38:01,350
来啊
Do it!

1263
01:38:13,490 --> 01:38:14,530
动手吧
Do it.

1264
01:38:16,310 --> 01:38:17,700
不
No!

1265
01:38:24,410 --> 01:38:26,170
