I'm not gonna let this happen to you.

1266
01:38:49,390 --> 01:38:50,790
没关系。
It's okay.

1267
01:39:08,800 --> 01:39:10,490
别挡路 就呆在这儿
Get out of the way. Stay here.

1268
01:39:10,630 --> 01:39:11,910
别往前
Just stay back.

1269
01:39:15,490 --> 01:39:16,450
劳里
Laurie!

1270
01:39:47,180 --> 01:39:48,190
迈克尔
Michael.

1271
01:39:49,710 --> 01:39:50,670
他死了
He's dead.

1272
01:39:54,690 --> 01:39:55,840
还没死透呢
Not dead enough.

1273
01:39:57,440 --> 01:39:58,630
我们不该这样
This isn't how we do it.

1274
01:40:00,410 --> 01:40:01,850
- 你真是疯了 - 你在干什么？
- You're all crazy. -  What are you doing?

1275
01:40:02,500 --> 01:40:03,430
你要带他去哪儿？
Where are you taking him?

1276
01:40:03,450 --> 01:40:05,780
哈顿菲尔德是时候从伤痛中走出来了
Time for Haddonfield to start healing.

1277
01:40:05,810 --> 01:40:07,250
让大家都看看吧
Let's show them all.

1278
01:40:12,030 --> 01:40:13,340
事情不该这样
This is not how it works.

1279
01:40:14,610 --> 01:40:15,860
就是今晚
It is tonight.

1280
01:40:16,710 --> 01:40:17,940
呃，加强无线电静默。
Uh, stronger on radio silence.

1281
01:40:17,960 --> 01:40:19,430
这是新的指令
That's got to be a command.

1282
01:40:19,460 --> 01:40:21,130
- 收到 - 收到
-Copy that. - Copy.

1283
01:40:21,150 --> 01:40:22,280
走吧
Let's go.

1284
01:42:51,700 --> 01:42:53,010
迈克尔·迈尔斯的尸体
The body of Michael Myers

1285
01:42:53,030 --> 01:42:55,380
已在一次午夜游行中被处置
was disposed of in a midnight procession.

1286
01:42:56,080 --> 01:42:58,720
没有任何的墓碑和纪念碑
There would be no tombstone, no memorial.

1287
01:42:59,350 --> 01:43:01,020
所有的谜已经解开
The mysteries were put to bed,

1288
01:43:01,390 --> 01:43:04,390
我们讲述的故事也将消逝在时间之中
and the story as we told it was to fade with time.

1289
01:43:09,150 --> 01:43:11,220
你对科里的怀疑是对的
You were right about Corey.

1290
01:43:13,760 --> 01:43:15,760
我知道是他杀了那些人
I know he killed those people.

1291
01:43:20,900 --> 01:43:22,750
他被邪恶吞噬了
He was consumed by evil.

1292
01:43:27,710 --> 01:43:29,540
哈顿菲尔德的事件
The events of Haddonfield

1293
01:43:29,850 --> 01:43:32,550
曾带来了如此多的暴力和鲜血
that created so much violence and bloodshed

1294
01:43:33,580 --> 01:43:34,960
现在终于结束了
finally had resolve.

1295
01:43:42,040 --> 01:43:43,890
报告中确当 迈克尔·迈尔斯
 Reports now confirm that Michael Myers

1296
01:43:43,920 --> 01:43:47,280
是在一起袭击未遂的事件中被反杀的
has indeed been killed dead after an attempted assault

1297
01:43:47,310 --> 01:43:49,990
被袭击对象是哈登菲尔德居民劳里·斯特罗德
of Haddonfield resident Laurie Strode.

1298
01:43:50,480 --> 01:43:52,890
一个奇迹般的生存故事
What an incredible story of survival

1299
01:43:53,230 --> 01:43:56,210
在我们的社区经历了几十年的动荡后
through decades of disturbances in our local community.

1300
01:43:56,230 --> 01:43:57,020
终于…
Finally...

1301
01:44:03,350 --> 01:44:05,260
新的开始就在眼前
New beginnings lay ahead.

1302
01:44:06,910 --> 01:44:08,620
我们都禁受了恐惧
Fear moves through all of us,

1303
01:44:09,290 --> 01:44:11,230
但我们可以自己决定 何时投降
and we decide when to surrender.

1304
01:44:13,310 --> 01:44:15,360
我已经与自己的恶魔人告别
I've said goodbye to my boogeyman,

1305
01:44:16,580 --> 01:44:18,680
但邪恶永远不会消亡
but the truth is evil doesn't die.

1306
01:44:20,230 --> 01:44:21,540
只是以另一种形式出现
It changes shape.

1307
01:44:40,950 --> 01:44:42,910
我希望你知道 我一直想着你
I wanted you to know I was thinking about you.

1308
01:44:44,110 --> 01:44:45,840
我想感谢你的壮举
I want to thank you for what you did.

1309
01:44:49,200 --> 01:44:50,060
送给你的
Enjoy.

1310
01:45:01,800 --> 01:45:05,510
再给我讲讲你之前说的樱花的故事吧
What was it you were saying about those cherry blossoms?
